msgctxt "#31214"
msgid "Resets the default background provided with Aeon Tajo."
msgstr "Huweka upya usuli chaguo-msingi uliotolewa na Aeon Tajo."

msgctxt "#31215"
msgid "Show the coloured version of the icons rather than the monochrome version."
msgstr "Onyesha toleo la rangi la ikoni badala ya toleo la monochrome."

msgctxt "#31216"
msgid "Displays background and fanart images with a subtle motion effect across the screen."
msgstr "Huonyesha mandharinyuma na picha za fanart zilizo na athari ndogo ya mwendo kwenye skrini."

msgctxt "#31217"
msgid "Displays a list in the video views featuring thumbnail images of the main actors from the movie or TV show's cast."
msgstr "Huonyesha orodha katika mionekano ya video iliyo na vijipicha vya waigizaji wakuu kutoka kwa waigizaji wa filamu au kipindi cha televisheni."

msgctxt "#31218"
msgid "Search the Studio Icons add-on for logo images of the film studios of the movie/TV show, and if found, display them while browsing the video views."
msgstr "Tafuta aikoni za Studio programu jalizi kwa picha za nembo za studio za filamu za kipindi cha televisheni, na zikipatikana, zionyeshe wakati wa kuvinjari mionekano ya video."

msgctxt "#31219"
msgid "Search for the album's record label logo using the RecordLabel Icons addon, and if found, display it when browsing the music album views."
msgstr "Tafuta nembo ya lebo ya rekodi ya albamu kwa kutumia Icons za RecordLabel, na ikipatikana, ionyeshe wakati wa kuvinjari mionekano ya albamu ya muziki."

msgctxt "#31220"
msgid "Show rating"
msgstr "Onyesha ukadiriaji"

msgctxt "#31221"
msgid "Show artist clearart"
msgstr "Onyesha uwazi wa msanii"

msgctxt "#31222"
msgid "Show CD"
msgstr "Onyesha CD"

msgctxt "#31223"
msgid "Show Time"
msgstr "Onyesha Wakati"

msgctxt "#31224"
msgid "Animated posters"
msgstr "Mabango yaliyohuishwa"

msgctxt "#31225"
msgid "Normal posters"
msgstr "Mabango ya kawaida"

msgctxt "#31226"
msgid "Extra posters"
msgstr "Mabango ya ziada"

msgctxt "#31227"
msgid "Sets the transparency level of the home menu widgets."
msgstr "Huweka kiwango cha uwazi cha wijeti za menyu ya nyumbani."

msgctxt "#31228"
msgid "Displays main menu options in a vertical layout instead of a horizontal one."
msgstr "Huonyesha chaguo za menyu kuu katika mpangilio wima badala ya ule wa mlalo."

msgctxt "#31229"
msgid "Set another video file as startup intro"
msgstr "Weka faili nyingine ya video kama utangulizi wa kuanza"

msgctxt "#31230"
msgid "Choose another video file to play when Kodi starts instead of Aeon Tajo default. It's recommended to choose a short one. To stop playback and start using Kodi right away, click or press any arrow key."
msgstr "Chagua faili nyingine ya video ya kucheza Kodi inapoanza badala ya chaguomsingi ya Aeon Tajo.Inashauriwa kuchagua moja fupi.Ili kuacha kucheza tena na kuanza kutumia Kodi mara moja, bofya au ubonyeze kitufe chochote cha kishale."

msgctxt "#31231"
msgid "Plays an intro video when launching Kodi"
msgstr "Hucheza video ya utangulizi wakati wa kuzindua Kodi"

msgctxt "#31232"
msgid "Clear current intro video file and back to default"
msgstr "Futa faili ya video ya utangulizi ya sasa na urudi kwa chaguomsingi"

msgctxt "#31233"
msgid "Clear the intro video file selected by the user and back to Aeon Tajo's default."
msgstr "Futa faili ya video ya utangulizi iliyochaguliwa na mtumiaji na urudi kwa chaguomsingi la Aeon Tajo."

msgctxt "#31234"
msgid "Adds a layer that simulates falling snow on all Kodi screens, with four available intensity levels."
msgstr "Huongeza safu inayoiga theluji inayoanguka kwenye skrini zote za Kodi, na viwango vinne vya ukubwa vinavyopatikana."

msgctxt "#31235"
msgid "Override the current home menu backgrounds with this one"
msgstr "Batilisha mandharinyuma ya sasa ya menyu ya nyumbani na hii"

msgctxt "#31236"
msgid "The background selections made in the Setup Main Menu screen will be preserved. Disabling this option will restore all previous backgrounds. This option is particularly designed for use during special seasons."
msgstr "Chaguo za usuli zilizofanywa kwenye skrini ya Menyu Kuu ya Kuweka zitahifadhiwa.Kuzima chaguo hili kutarejesha usuli wote wa awali.Chaguo hili limeundwa hasa kwa matumizi wakati wa misimu maalum."

