msgctxt "#31400"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE INTERFACE SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Change the skin · Set language and region · Setup remote controls[CR]Set up a screensaver · Setup master lock"
msgstr "[B]WEKEBISHA MIPANGILIO YA INTERFACE[/B][CR][CR]Badilisha ngozi · Weka lugha na eneo · Weka vidhibiti vya mbali[CR]Weka kihifadhi skrini · Sanidi kufuli kuu"

msgctxt "#31401"
msgid "Menu - press 'OK'"
msgstr "Menyu - bonyeza 'Sawa'"

msgctxt "#31402"
msgid "Enable startup video intro"
msgstr "Washa utangulizi wa video ya kuanzia"

msgctxt "#31405"
msgid "[B]MONITOR YOUR SYSTEM[/B][CR][CR]Check out your hardware · Monitor CPU usage[CR]Check Kodi revision number"
msgstr "[B]FUATILIA MFUMO WAKO[/B][CR][CR]Angalia maunzi yako · Fuatilia matumizi ya CPU[CR]Angalia nambari ya marekebisho ya Kodi"

msgctxt "#31406"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE SYSTEM SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Setup and calibrate displays · Configure audio output · [CR]Set power saving options · Enable debugging"
msgstr "[B]WEKEBISHA MIPANGILIO YA MFUMO[/B][CR][CR]Weka na urekebishe maonyesho · Sanidi utoaji wa sauti · [CR]Weka chaguo za kuokoa nishati · Washa utatuzi"

msgctxt "#31407"
msgid "[B]SETUP PROFILES[/B][CR][CR]Setup and manage user profiles · Enable login screen[CR]Change password · Add a profile picture"
msgstr "[B]WEKA WASIFU[/B][CR][CR]Weka na udhibiti wasifu wa mtumiaji · Washa skrini ya kuingia[CR]Badilisha nenosiri · Ongeza picha ya wasifu"

msgctxt "#31409"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE TV SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Change full screen info · Manage EPG data settings"
msgstr "[B]WEKEBISHA MIPANGILIO YA TV[/B][CR][CR]Badilisha maelezo ya skrini nzima · Dhibiti mipangilio ya data ya EPG"

msgctxt "#31410"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE SERVICE SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Setup control of Kodi via UPnP and HTTP · Configure file sharing[CR]Enable Zeroconf · Configure AirPlay"
msgstr "[B]WEKEBISHA MIPANGILIO YA HUDUMA[/B][CR][CR]Kuweka udhibiti wa Kodi kupitia UPnP na HTTP · Weka mipangilio ya kushiriki faili[CR]Washa Zeroconf · Sanidi AirPlay"

msgctxt "#31412"
msgid "Select section"
msgstr "Chagua sehemu"

msgctxt "#31413"
msgid "Local subtitle available"
msgstr "Manukuu ya eneo lako yanapatikana"

msgctxt "#31414"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE PLAYER SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Configure video playback · Configure music playback · Configure picture slideshow[CR]Configure video language and subtitles"
msgstr "[B]WEKA MIPANGILIO YA KICHEZAJI[/B][CR][CR]Sanidi uchezaji wa video · Sanidi uchezaji wa muziki · Sanidi onyesho la slaidi la picha[CR]Sanidi lugha ya video na manukuu"

msgctxt "#31415"
msgid "[B]CONFIGURE MEDIA SETTINGS[/B][CR][CR]Set default select action · Configure file list options · Configure metadata options[CR]Manage databases"
msgstr "[B]WEKA MIPANGILIO YA MEDIA[/B][CR][CR]Weka kitendo cha kuchagua chaguo-msingi · Sanidi chaguo za orodha ya faili · Sanidi chaguo za metadata[CR]Dhibiti hifadhidata"

msgctxt "#31421"
msgid "Select your Kodi user profile[CR]to login and continue"
msgstr "Chagua wasifu wako wa mtumiaji wa Kodi[CR]ili kuingia na kuendelea"

msgctxt "#31427"
msgid "Skin Shortcuts is responsible for handling all aspects of the main menu."
msgstr "Njia za mkato za ngozi ni wajibu wa kushughulikia vipengele vyote vya menyu kuu."

msgctxt "#31428"
msgid "The Grab Fanart script provides the random fanart slideshows for the main menu."
msgstr "Hati ya Grab Fanart hutoa maonyesho ya slaidi nasibu ya fanart kwa menyu kuu."

msgctxt "#31429"
msgid "Library Data Provider is a service that runs in the background to provide library data for widgets and live backgrounds as well as playlist statistics for infolines."
msgstr "Mtoa Data wa Maktaba ni huduma inayofanya kazi chinichini ili kutoa data ya maktaba ya wijeti na usuli wa moja kwa moja pamoja na takwimu za orodha za kucheza za laini."

msgctxt "#31430"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white studio icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "Nyongeza ya picha ya nyenzo kwa ajili ya kuonyesha aikoni chaguo-msingi za studio nyeupe kwenye ngozi."

msgctxt "#31431"
msgid "Resource image addon for displaying the default white recording label icons throughout the skin."
msgstr "Nyongeza ya picha ya nyenzo kwa ajili ya kuonyesha aikoni chaguo-msingi za lebo nyeupe za kurekodi kwenye ngozi."

msgctxt "#31432"
msgid "Provides numerous Widget options and extended cast and crew metadata."
msgstr "Hutoa chaguo nyingi za Wijeti na metadata iliyopanuliwa ya utumaji na wafanyakazi."

msgctxt "#31433"
msgid "Skin Info Service is used to display movie set information throughout the skin."
msgstr "Huduma ya Maelezo ya Ngozi hutumiwa kuonyesha maelezo ya seti ya filamu kwenye ngozi."

msgctxt "#31434"
msgid "Check MP3 Theme checks whether the user has put a theme.mp3 file in the corresponding movie/TV show folder to be played when browsing."
msgstr "Angalia Mandhari ya MP3 hukagua ikiwa mtumiaji ameweka faili ya theme.mp3 kwenye folda inayolingana ya filamu/kipindi cha televisheni cha kuchezwa wakati wa kuvinjari."

msgctxt "#31450"
msgid "  •  Open Settings "
msgstr "• Fungua Mipangilio"

msgctxt "#31451"
msgid "  •  Click to Install"
msgstr "• Bofya ili Kusakinisha"

msgctxt "#31473"
msgid "Aeon Tajo Helper provides the data to display the cast for movies and TV shows."
msgstr "Aeon Tajo Helper hutoa data ya kuonyesha waigizaji wa filamu na vipindi vya televisheni."

msgctxt "#31474"
msgid "CU LRC Lyrics is used to download, sync, and display lyrics during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "Nyimbo za CU LRC hutumiwa kupakua, kusawazisha na kuonyesha maneno wakati wa uchezaji wa muziki wa skrini nzima."

msgctxt "#31475"
msgid "Play Trailer makes possible to play movie trailers through a context menu. "
msgstr "Play Trailer hurahisisha kucheza vionjo vya filamu kupitia menyu ya muktadha."

msgctxt "#31476"
msgid "Allows the use of Youtube to play trailers and other videos."
msgstr "Inaruhusu matumizi ya YouTube kucheza trela na video zingine."

msgctxt "#31477"
msgid "Provides some cast actress images to be shown in video views."
msgstr "Hutoa baadhi ya picha za mwigizaji wa kuigiza kuonyeshwa katika mionekano ya video."

msgctxt "#31478"
msgid "Artist Slideshow is used to display artist fanart for both the home screen and during fullscreen music playback."
msgstr "Onyesho la Slaidi la Msanii hutumiwa kuonyesha ushabiki wa msanii kwa skrini ya kwanza na wakati wa uchezaji wa muziki wa skrini nzima."

msgctxt "#31479"
msgid "AutoCompletion provides suggestions to be selected while using the virtual keyboard."
msgstr "Ukamilishaji Kiotomatiki hutoa mapendekezo ya kuchaguliwa unapotumia kibodi pepe."

msgctxt "#31480"
msgid "Library Editor Script uses JSON to directly edit your database information."
msgstr "Hati ya Kuhariri Maktaba hutumia JSON kuhariri moja kwa moja maelezo yako ya hifadhidata."

msgctxt "#31481"
msgid "Global Search makes possible to search among all the items (movies, TV shows, music, actors, etc.) in your collection."
msgstr "Utafutaji wa Ulimwenguni humuwezesha kutafuta kati ya vipengee vyote (filamu, vipindi vya televisheni, muziki, waigizaji, n.k.) katika mkusanyiko wako."

msgctxt "#31501"
msgid "Channel group"
msgstr "Kikundi cha kituo"

msgctxt "#31502"
msgid "Live TV"
msgstr "TV ya moja kwa moja"

msgctxt "#31503"
msgid "Add Group"
msgstr "Ongeza Kikundi"

msgctxt "#31504"
msgid "Rename Group"
msgstr "Badilisha Kikundi jina"

msgctxt "#31505"
msgid "Delete Group"
msgstr "Futa Kikundi"

msgctxt "#31506"
msgid "Available[CR]Groups"
msgstr "Inapatikana[CR]Vikundi"

msgctxt "#31511"
msgid "Channel Options"
msgstr "Chaguzi za Kituo"

msgctxt "#31512"
msgid "Show similar movies in Shelf 3D view"
msgstr "Onyesha filamu zinazofanana katika mwonekano wa Shelf 3D"

msgctxt "#31901"
msgid "36 Hour Forecast"
msgstr "Utabiri wa Saa 36"

msgctxt "#31902"
msgid "Hourly Forecast"
msgstr "Utabiri wa Kila Saa"

msgctxt "#31903"
msgid "Weekend Forecast"
msgstr "Utabiri wa Wikendi"

msgctxt "#31904"
msgid "10 Day Forecast"
msgstr "Utabiri wa Siku 10"

msgctxt "#31908"
msgid "Chance of Precipitation"
msgstr "Uwezekano wa Kunyesha"

msgctxt "#31909"
msgid "Fetching forecast info..."
msgstr "Inaleta maelezo ya utabiri..."

msgctxt "#31910"
msgid "Map & Alerts"
msgstr "Ramani na Arifa"

msgctxt "#31911"
msgid "Setup the Aeon Tajo main menu"
msgstr "Sanidi menyu kuu ya Aeon Tajo"

msgctxt "#31912"
msgid "Customize the main menu with widgets, backgrounds and statistics. Add your own custom main menu items."
msgstr "Geuza kukufaa menyu kuu ukitumia wijeti, usuli na takwimu.Ongeza vitu vyako maalum vya menyu kuu."

msgctxt "#31913"
msgid "Aeon Tajo main menu vertical position"
msgstr "Nafasi ya wima ya menyu kuu ya Aeon Tajo"

msgctxt "#31914"
msgid "Change the vertical position of the main menu. Default is centered on screen."
msgstr "Badilisha nafasi ya wima ya menyu kuu.Chaguo-msingi imewekwa kwenye skrini."

msgctxt "#31915"
msgid "Navigation style for horizontal lists"
msgstr "Mtindo wa kusogeza kwa orodha za mlalo"

msgctxt "#31916"
msgid "Change the way horizontal lists scroll in Aeon Tajo. Default will scroll lists in a cycle. \"Fixed\" are lists with a beginning and end."
msgstr "Badilisha jinsi orodha za mlalo zinavyosonga katika Aeon Tajo.Chaguomsingi itasogeza orodha katika mzunguko.\"Zisizohamishika\" ni orodha zenye mwanzo na mwisho."

msgctxt "#31917"
msgid "When enabled text scrolls automatically. When disabled manual scrolling is required. Note that most textboxes don't have a manual button."
msgstr "Maandishi yakiwezeshwa yanasonga kiotomatiki.Unapozimwa kusogeza kwa mikono kunahitajika.Kumbuka kuwa visanduku vingi vya maandishi havina kitufe cha mwongozo."

msgctxt "#31918"
msgid "Projects the current playing video on the background behind the panels."
msgstr "Hutengeneza video inayocheza sasa kwenye usuli nyuma ya vidirisha."

msgctxt "#31919"
msgid "Projects the visualisation on the background behind the panels when music is played."
msgstr "Hutengeneza taswira kwenye usuli nyuma ya vidirisha muziki unapochezwa."

msgctxt "#31920"
msgid "Displays a widget on the Home screen with media information when music is playing."
msgstr "Huonyesha wijeti kwenye Skrini ya kwanza yenye maelezo ya midia wakati muziki unachezwa."

msgctxt "#31921"
msgid "Displays a widget on the Home screen with media information when a movie or episode is playing."
msgstr "Huonyesha wijeti kwenye Skrini ya kwanza yenye maelezo ya midia wakati filamu au kipindi kinacheza."

msgctxt "#31922"
msgid "This enables custom genre backgrounds when browsing through the videolibrary's genre node. Filenames should match the genre label. Extension must be .jpg."
msgstr "Hii huwezesha usuli wa aina maalum wakati wa kuvinjari nodi ya aina ya maktaba ya video.Majina ya faili yanapaswa kuendana na lebo ya aina.Kiendelezi lazima kiwe .jpg."

msgctxt "#31923"
msgid "Set a default select action to enable this item."
msgstr "Weka kitendo cha chaguo-msingi ili kuwezesha kipengee hiki."

msgctxt "#31924"
msgid "This enables custom genre backgrounds when browsing through the musiclibrary's genre node. Filenames should match the genre label. Extension must be .jpg."
msgstr "Hii huwezesha asili ya aina maalum wakati wa kuvinjari nodi ya aina ya maktaba ya muziki.Majina ya faili yanapaswa kuendana na lebo ya aina.Kiendelezi lazima kiwe .jpg."

msgctxt "#31925"
msgid "Pick one of the preset backgrounds or set your own images as the menu items background."
msgstr "Chagua mojawapo ya mandharinyuma yaliyowekwa mapema au uweke picha zako kama usuli wa vipengee vya menyu."

msgctxt "#31926"
msgid "Select add-ons, playlists or favourites. Choose 'Custom' for any of Kodi's built-in functions. (http://kodi.wiki/?title=List_of_Built_In_Functions)"
msgstr "Chagua programu jalizi, orodha za kucheza au vipendwa.Chagua 'Custom' kwa vitendaji vyovyote vilivyojengewa ndani vya Kodi.(http://kodi.wiki/?title=List_of_Built_In_Functions)"

msgctxt "#31927"
msgid "Resets all above values to their defaults."
msgstr "Huweka upya thamani zote zilizo hapo juu kuwa chaguomsingi zao."

msgctxt "#31928"
msgid "Aeon Tajo main menu layout"
msgstr "Mpangilio wa menyu kuu ya Aeon Tajo"

msgctxt "#31929"
msgid "This setting defines how much items will be visible on the main menu. Options are 3 items or 5 items."
msgstr "Mpangilio huu unafafanua ni kiasi gani cha vitu vitaonekana kwenye menyu kuu.Chaguo ni vitu 3 au vitu 5."

msgctxt "#31930"
msgid "Choose a widget to display on the Home screen to have easy access to content from the library."
msgstr "Chagua wijeti ya kuonyesha kwenye Skrini ya kwanza ili kupata ufikiaji rahisi wa maudhui kutoka kwenye maktaba."

msgctxt "#31931"
msgid "Video plot preference"
msgstr "Upendeleo wa mpangilio wa video"

msgctxt "#31932"
msgid "Show plot outline in the library views and full plot in the video information dialog or vice versa. Falls back to full plot if no outline is available."
msgstr "Onyesha muhtasari wa njama katika mionekano ya maktaba na njama kamili katika mazungumzo ya habari ya video au kinyume chake.Inarudi kwa mpangilio kamili ikiwa hakuna muhtasari unaopatikana."

msgctxt "#31933"
msgid "Select an item to display on the left top of the main menu"
msgstr "Chagua kipengee cha kuonyesha kwenye sehemu ya juu ya kushoto ya menyu kuu"

msgctxt "#31935"
msgid "Switch places with another menu item. Opens a dialog with a list of menu items to choose from."
msgstr "Badilisha maeneo na kipengee kingine cha menyu.Hufungua kidirisha chenye orodha ya vipengee vya menyu vya kuchagua."

msgctxt "#31937"
msgid "Show the RSS feed on the bottom or top of the screen, depending on main menu position. Enabling this setting makes the submenu permanently visible."
msgstr "Onyesha mipasho ya RSS chini au juu ya skrini, kulingana na nafasi ya menyu kuu.Kuwasha mpangilio huu hufanya menyu ndogo ionekane kabisa."

msgctxt "#31938"
msgid "Enables extra information in the TV show library, like TV show status, next / latest episode, etc. Depends on TV Show Next Aired add-on."
msgstr "Huwasha maelezo ya ziada katika maktaba ya kipindi cha televisheni, kama vile hali ya kipindi cha TV, kipindi kifuatacho / kipya zaidi, n.k. Inategemea programu jalizi ya Kipindi Kinachofuata cha TV."

msgctxt "#31939"
msgid "Hide Infopanel on scrolling"
msgstr "Ficha Infopanel wakati wa kusogeza"

msgctxt "#31940"
msgid "Hides the infopanel for Showcase and Landscape view (if activated) while scrolling through the library. Set the amount of seconds to wait for the infopanel to appear when scrolling is stopped."
msgstr "Huficha paneli ya maelezo kwa Mwonekano wa Maonyesho na Mandhari (ikiwa imewashwa) wakati wa kuvinjari maktaba.Weka kiasi cha sekunde kusubiri infopanel kuonekana wakati kusogeza kumekomeshwa."

msgctxt "#31941"
msgid "Kiosk mode"
msgstr "Hali ya skrini nzima"

msgctxt "#31942"
msgid "Disables the slide out menu (media menu) in the library as well as certain buttons in the media information dialogs. (Requires restart to take effect)"
msgstr "Huzima menyu ya slaidi (menu ya midia) kwenye maktaba pamoja na vitufe fulani kwenye vidadisi vya habari vya midia.(Inahitaji kuanzishwa upya ili kuanza kutumika)"

msgctxt "#31943"
msgid "Watched status indicator"
msgstr "Kiashiria cha hali iliyotazamwa"

msgctxt "#31944"
msgid "Choose which overlays to show on thumbs in icon based views. Note that the \"Resume\" flag takes precedent over any watched status."
msgstr "Chagua ni viwekeleo vipi vya kuonyesha kwenye vidole gumba katika mionekano kulingana na ikoni.Kumbuka kuwa alama ya \"Rejea\" inachukua kipaumbele juu ya hali yoyote inayotazamwa."

msgctxt "#31945"
msgid "This toggles the layout of the List view. Default is a 7 item layout with extended info, \"Slim List\" is a 14 item, more basic layout"
msgstr "Hii hugeuza mpangilio wa mwonekano wa Orodha.Chaguomsingi ni mpangilio wa vipengee 7 na maelezo yaliyopanuliwa, \"Orodha Nyembamba\" ni kipengee 14, mpangilio wa msingi zaidi."

msgctxt "#31950"
msgid "WEATHER"
msgstr "HALI YA HEWA"

msgctxt "#31951"
msgid "PICTURES"
msgstr "PICHA"

msgctxt "#31952"
msgid "LIVE TV"
msgstr "TV ya moja kwa moja"

