msgctxt "#31290"
msgid "Thanks for using Aeon Tajo—I really hope you’re enjoying it. Creating and maintaining a Kodi skin like this takes hundreds of hours of work. If Aeon Tajo is something you enjoy and find useful, supporting it helps me keep working on it and ensures it can continue evolving in the future. [CR][CR]If you decide to do so, you’ll receive frequent updates with new features and bug fixes, along with videos, media packs, and easy-to-follow articles with detailed tips to help you get the most out of everything Aeon Tajo has to offer, together with my sincere gratitude for your support. [CR][CR]For more information, visit [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] and search for the creator [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], or go to [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR][CR]Thanks!"
msgstr "Asante kwa kutumia Aeon Tajo—natumai unaifurahia.Kuunda na kudumisha ngozi ya Kodi kama hii inachukua mamia ya masaa ya kazi.Ikiwa Aeon Tajo ni kitu ambacho unakifurahia na unachokiona kuwa muhimu, kukiunga mkono hunisaidia kuendelea kulifanyia kazi na kuhakikisha kwamba kinaweza kuendelea kubadilika katika siku zijazo.[CR][CR]Ukiamua kufanya hivyo, utapokea masasisho ya mara kwa mara yenye vipengele vipya na kurekebishwa kwa hitilafu, pamoja na video, vifurushi vya maudhui na makala ambayo ni rahisi kufuata yenye vidokezo vya kina vya kukusaidia kunufaika zaidi na kila kitu ambacho Aeon Tajo anaweza kutoa, pamoja na shukrani zangu za dhati kwa usaidizi wako.[CR][CR]Kwa maelezo zaidi, tembelea [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] na utafute mtayarishi [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], au uende kwenye [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR]Thanks.[CR]!"

